{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of checkbox","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for  "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"checkboxes"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSCheckbox"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSCheckboxItem"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllCheckboxComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide all tokens to the users."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeCheckboxComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CheckboxComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"checkboxes","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"